title: Department of Revenue's Coos Bay office closed for training (DOR - Oregon Department of Revenue) ...
text: ( Source : DOR - Oregon Department of Revenue ) SALEM , Oregon-The Oregon Department of Revenue's Coos Bay satellite office will be closed on the following dates so staff can attend training: · September 15-16. · October 12-16. · November 9-10 .
